text: Praden () is a village in the municipality of Tschiertschen-Praden in the district Plessur in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. The formerly independent municipality merged with Tschiertschen to form Tschiertschen- Praden on January 1, 2009. Category:Villages in Graubünden Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
title: Praden
